sourcesContent: import{jsx as r}from"react/jsx-runtime";import{ComponentClassNames as o}from"../shared/constants.js";import"../Icon/Icon.js";import"classnames";import"../View/View.js";import"react";import{IconCheckCircle as c}from"../Icon/icons/IconCheckCircle.js";import{IconError as n}from"../Icon/icons/IconError.js";import{IconInfo as s}from"../Icon/icons/IconInfo.js";import{IconWarning as e}from"../Icon/icons/IconWarning.js";const t=({variation:t})=>{switch(t){case"info":return r(s,{className:o.AlertIcon});case"error":return r(n,{className:o.AlertIcon});case"warning":return r(e,{className:o.AlertIcon});case"success":return r(c,{className:o.AlertIcon});default:return null}};t.displayName="AlertIcon";export{t as AlertIcon};
